"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10015965\">",
"      What do I need to tell my doctor before I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10015970\">",
"      What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10015971\">",
"      What are some side effects of this drug?",
"     </a>",
